{"tid":2391458,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"自由時報：內部視訊曝光！臉書自承權力大 配合拜登政府帶風向","createTime":"2021-02-02T08:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T03:26:25.000Z","uid":276356,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"70e0493f1e32f55a07fa60ef07e9ca693b7eafc5","tid":2391458,"uid":276356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3429796\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3429796&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BAoJw9ynFthkhoOYQBA%2BRXM%3D&h=33dae933\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3429796&h=56704005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3429796</a><br />\n<br />\n〔編譯陳成良／綜合報導〕美國保守派組織「真相項目」（Project Veritas）1月31日公佈「追哨人」提供的臉書內部視訊，洩漏臉書執行長札克伯格有意在重大議題上與拜登政府合作，配合帶風向，同時臉書高管也自承「權力太大」。<br />\n<br />\n此前，《路透》上月踢爆Google、臉書和推特等科技巨頭在美國大選後，幕後運作安插人馬到拜登團隊中擔任高級職務，以便影響美國政府做出對自己有利的政策。<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「真相項目」日前也曾公開推特創辦人杜錫（Jack Dorsey）及高管們聲稱要加強言論審查的視訊證據，該項目負責人奧基夫（James O』Keefe）繼續曝光臉書的內部機密。提供該視訊的臉書團隊成員表示，自己仍在臉書工作，並願意繼續揭露札克伯格及其組織的腐敗。<br />\n<br />\n在這段視訊中，札克伯格表示，在透過嚴格的言論審查實現了前總統川普的權力移交後，他希望在武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，Covid-19）疫情的輿論導向上，繼續與拜登政府合作。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「拜登總統在上任第一天，已經簽署了一些行政命令，涉及我們作為一家公司所相當關心的領域。」「我期待有機會與新一屆政府合作，從因應Covid的一些他們最優先的事項上，進行合作。」<br />\n<br />\n視訊中，臉書全球事務副總裁克萊格（Nick Clegg）承認，世界上很多領導人，包括墨西哥總統、俄羅斯反對派領袖納瓦尼（Alexei Navalny）、德國總理梅克爾等，都對封殺川普的言論表示不安，這說明臉書已經擁有太大權力。<br />\n<br />\n札克伯格被控在關鍵搖擺州投入巨額資金，干涉美國大選，他去年11月17日曾透過視訊參加參院聽證會，就封殺拜登父子醜聞等言論審查方式，提出說明。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》1月25日進一步報導，2020年科技業遊說支出，臉書近2000萬美元（約新台幣5.6億）蟬聯冠軍，以灑銀彈策略迎接新一屆政府以及對它們業務的新審查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JamesOKeefeIII/status/1356059627616657414?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJamesOKeefeIII%2Fstatus%2F1356059627616657414%3Fs%3D19&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BAoJw9ynFthkhoOYQBA%2BRXM%3D&h=85bf41ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJamesOKeefeIII%2Fstatus%2F1356059627616657414%3Fs%3D19&h=1a507e61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JamesOKeefeIII/status/1356059627616657414?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"20b53060e25cef582801a685d2eb29d2486017fc","tid":2391458,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912e9992a0c687f6676feccaec4d5af8373f978e","tid":2391458,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:01:03.000Z","msg":"奶支那閪既豬閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e375525dcd44e9d0c86475fc1a0d5222dc606f6","tid":2391458,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死豬閪"},{"pid":"b8cc99c64517d868697f2a09be065e39724df8c6","tid":2391458,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:02:19.000Z","msg":"Dirty KIKE"},{"pid":"46941c4f152f6a308659da8baee4bbae6e5eb15b","tid":2391458,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:15:17.000Z","msg":"睇班撚樣講嘢就知幾撚離地"},{"pid":"ffec4c503b2c354bd2c9c9546342c2b2ccb85c16","tid":2391458,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶共狗食屎啦"},{"pid":"31f353bf9776a837c6842f598220c944e544d0ed","tid":2391458,"uid":60057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:32:01.000Z","msg":"佢個樣愈來愈衰，以前都冇咁人乾，有少少笑容，依家完全冇左靈魂咁"},{"pid":"47b4e382f6d31c48b0d8a97bbd